<P>
WELFARE PROGRAMS -- UNITED STATES; WELFARE PROGRAMS -- LOS ANGELES; HOMELESS -- 
LOS ANGELES; HOMELESS -- UNITED STATES; SHELTERS; FOOD; EMERGENCIES; MAYORS 
</P>
