<P>
YOUTHS TO PERFORM IN 'LAS POSADAS' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
LONG BEACH 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Escuela de Nuevo Canto and the Long Beach Council of the League of United 
Latin American Citizens will present "Las Posadas Navidenas" from 4 to 7 p.m. 
on Saturdayat Drake Park, 951 Maine Ave., Long Beach. 
</P>
<P>
"Las Posadas" will include music, songs and a theatrical presentation performed 
by Latino youths. The singers are from the Escuela de Nuevo Canto, a group of 
