<P>
MEDICARE; HEALTH CARE FINANCING ADMINISTRATION (U.S.); MEDICAL CARE -- UNITED 
STATES; HOSPITALS -- UNITED STATES; AGED -- HEALTH; ORGAN TRANSPLANTS; DEATH 
RATES; HEALTH STATISTICS 
</P>
