PICTURE); RACIAL RELATIONS -- ALABAMA; RACIAL DISCRIMINATION; BOYCOTTS; ALABAMA 
-- TRANSPORTATION; BUSES; BLACKS -- ALABAMA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
