<HEADLINE>
<P>
HOT TOPICS: GIFT IDEAS OUT OF THE MOUTHS OF THE TEENS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Responses gathered by Janet Bester (Connelly), Dana Wilshin (Dana Hills), 
Eric Billigmeier (Esperanza), Sonal Kapadia (Irvine), Trisha Ginsburg (Los 
Alamitos), Ginny Chang (Santa Ana Valley) and Michael Chen (Valencia). 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Though Hanukkah gift giving has ended, there remains just a little more than a 
weekend to get in last-minute Christmas shopping. 
</P>
