<P>
Carson Float -- A story on Dec. 13 incorrectly reported that the Carson City 
Council voted to eliminate funding for a city float in future Rose parades. In 
fact, the council voted to notify parade officials of their interest in having 
a municipal float in the 1992 event. However, the council did not approve city 
funding for the float and some council members said the city will not make a 
financial commitment toward the cost of a float. 
