Kickback case -- The Times reported Tuesday that a components engineer for 
Hughes Aircraft Co. in Fullerton pleaded guilty in federal court to soliciting 
kickback payments from two subcontractors -- Bergquist Co. of Long Beach and 
Lyn-Tron Inc. of Burbank. The news item did not make clear that both companies 
