SOUTHLAND; 
</P>
<P>
GIONIS ASSAULT CASE A MISTRIAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Wire Services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
SANTA ANA 
</P>
