members take a break at Echo Park workout. From left are Alma Herrera, Patty 
Trejo, Rene Arellano and Sergio Lopez. ROBERT GABRIEL / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, COLOR, runners 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
